<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
Entity: assembly_module_join_terminal
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Assembly_module_macro_definition_mim.assembly_module_join_terminal">
<p>

An <b>assembly_module_join_terminal</b> is a type of <express_ref linkend="Assembly_module_usage_view:mim:Assembly_module_usage_view_mim.assembly_module_terminal"/> that implement the
ARM concept of  <express_ref linkend="Assembly_module_macro_definition:arm:Assembly_module_macro_definition_arm.Assembly_module_join_terminal"/>
</p></ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
Rule: component_terminal_to_assembly_module_join_terminal_assignment_unique_constraint
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Assembly_module_macro_definition_mim.component_terminal_to_assembly_module_join_terminal_assignment_unique_constraint">
<p>

The <b>component_terminal_to_assembly_module_join_terminal_assignment_unique_constraint</b>
rule constrains the  <express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.shape_aspect_relationship"/> population members, that fill the
role of ARM <express_ref linkend="Assembly_module_macro_definition:arm:Assembly_module_macro_definition_arm.Component_terminal_to_assembly_module_join_terminal_assignment"/>, so that
the ARM <express_ref linkend="Assembly_module_macro_definition:arm:Assembly_module_macro_definition_arm.Component_terminal_to_assembly_module_join_terminal_assignment.usage_view_terminal"/> attribute shall be unique within the population.
</p></ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
WR: component_terminal_to_assembly_module_join_terminal_assignment_unique_constraint.WR1
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Assembly_module_macro_definition_mim.component_terminal_to_assembly_module_join_terminal_assignment_unique_constraint.wr:WR1">
Every instance of  <express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.shape_aspect_relationship"/> with a name of
'component feature to physical usage view assignment' must have a unique  <express_ref linkend="Assembly_module_macro_definition:mim:Assembly_module_macro_definition_mim.assembly_module_join_terminal"/> entity
as the  <express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.shape_aspect_relationship"/>'s <express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.shape_aspect_relationship.relating_shape_aspect"/> attribute.
</ext_description>

